data.description: Exceptional Spacious 4/2.5 baths Home. Tile flooring throughout first floor and laminate wood floors on second floor. Upgraded Kitchen with wood cabinets, granite counters tops, glass tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances. Modern glass stair railing. Open concept great for family gatherings & making memories. Master bedroom has large walk-in closet and dual sinks. Large bedrooms & closets. Paved backyard with gazebo making it great for entertaining. Located on a street w/minimal traffic. Clubhouse designed for resort style living, social party room, state of the art gym, swimming pool & hot tub. Fabulous playground for children.
